title: Dez Bryant gets new pet monkey, names it Dallas Bryant
text: Dez Bryant gets new pet monkey, names it Dallas Bryant Comment By Katie Richcreek, Bleacher Report providencejournal.com By Katie Richcreek, Bleacher Report Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 11:14 AM By Katie Richcreek, Bleacher Report Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 11:14 AM Dez Bryant introduced his new pet to the world Wednesday, but it wasn't your traditional golden retriever. The Dallas Cowboys wide receiver instead went with a pet of the primate variety. Yes, it's a little monkey, and his name is Dallas Bryant. By Katie Richcreek, Bleacher Report providencejournal.com By Katie Richcreek, Bleacher Report Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 11:14 AM
